## compare the difference

<br>

```
t=$(mktemp --suffix .go)
echo 'package main
import "fmt"
func main(){fmt.Println("Hello, World!")}' > $t
go run $t
rm $t
```
<br>
or

<br>

```
gosh -e 'fmt.Println("Hello, World!")'
```

: 6 lines and 117 characters
: versus
: 1 line and 39 characters
: .
: One third of the typing
: .
: The code isn't hidden in a wall of text

