## Helpful parameters

Printing
<br>

```
gosh -pln '"Hello, World!"'
gosh -p '"Hello, World!\n"'
gosh -pf '"%20s\n", "Hello, World!"'
```

: We often print things so the -p params simplify that
: .
: -pln wraps its arguments in a call to fmt.Println
: -p uses fmt.Print
: -pf uses fmt.Printf

